Along the way you will find a small seldom-seen temple built on a rock in the ocean where its said that fertility prayers are answered.

strIntroduction: Go on a cultural spa tour in the island paradise of Bali! Rejuvenate your body and soul with luxurious spa treatments and a cleansing visit to a Balinese mangku.
